  "body": "This is the expansion pattern from design\n\n### Open expandable content\n`--pf-t--global--motion--duration--md` and \n`--pf-t--global--timing-function--decelerate`\n\n## Caret\nCaret icon rotates 90 degrees with a  \n`--pf-t--global--motion--duration--icon--default` and \n`--pf-t--global--timing-function--default`\n\n### Close expandable content\n`--pf-t--global--motion--duration--sm` and\n`--pf-t--global--timing-function--accelerate`\n\n## Caret\nCaret icon rotates -90 degrees with a  \n`--pf-t--global--motion--duration--icon--default` and \n`--pf-t--global--timing-function--default`",
